{% doc %}
  @prompt
    “Create a homepage section similar to Jockey’s ‘On-Trend Picks’.
    Include 5–7 sliding cards in one row with smooth auto-scroll and arrows on both sides.
    Each card should have:
    
    A background image (product image or gradient color)
    
    Bold heading (like ‘PANTS ON POINT’)
    
    Subheading or tagline (e.g., ‘Comfort you can count on’)
    
    A call-to-action button (‘Explore Now’)
    
    The design should have rounded card corners, clean typography, and pastel background colors (light blue, pink, beige).
    Use minimal shadows for depth and ensure it looks modern and mobile-responsive.
    The section title should be ‘ON-TREND PICKS’ with a subtitle ‘Explore Our Promising Line-Up’ centered above the slider.”
{% enddoc %}
